        Creates a TagMap from this builder.

      • buildScoped

        Scope buildScoped()
        Enters the scope of code where the TagMap created from this builder is in the current context and returns an object that represents that scope. The scope is exited when the returned object is closed.
        Returns:
        an object that defines a scope where the TagMap created from this builder is set to the current context.
        Since:
        0.1.0
